data.description: BACK ON THE MARKET, NO FAULT OF HOME. BUYER GOT COLD FEET. Welcome to 3612 Golden St., in the heart of Evans, Colorado. This charming home features 2 bedrooms and 1 bathroom, offering a perfect blend of comfort and simplicity.  Step outside to discover the expansive backyard, a haven for outdoor enthusiasts and garden lovers alike. A standout feature of this property is the spacious 3-car detached garage, providing ample room for vehicles, storage, or a workshop. Convenient alley access adds a touch of privacy and accessibility. Whether you're a first-time homebuyer or looking to downsize, 3612 Golden St. presents a wonderful opportunity to make a house your own cozy haven.
